			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2241959">
									

<p>I found Solace to be a thoroughly boring character, the references to other self-insert characters to be clunky, out-of-place, and self-indulgent, and the core principle did not strike me as particularly gripping.</p>
<p>As a result the attempts at any sort of emotional impact were dead on arrival.</p>
<p>Downvoted for all of the above.</p>

